summary: Winston Duke To Lead New Thriller Heroine
title: Winston Duke To Lead New Thriller Heroine
excerpt: Black Panther's breakout has another role. Check Empire for more.
description:
While it might seem odd to have a male actor starring in a film with that title, it’ll actually be a story shared between his character and a mother and domestic abuse survivor who moves into a new neighbourhood. Looking to put her traumatic past behind her, she runs into new trouble when she witness an Aryan gang kidnapping a local.

Duke is set to play her neighbour, a man who has built his own metal suit and takes on the Aryans.


…. the Iron Man reboot we didn’t realize we desperately wanted?

(Or, if I could still keep up with the DCU, Steel. John Henry Irons deserved better than what he got.)

title: La Famiglia
body:
read it on the AO3 at https://ift.tt/2P4toU2

by athletiger

The Stark Family is one of the largest and strongest crime syndicates on American soil, infamously known for their ruthlessness and their tight-knit community. Government files report that they produce black-market weapons and do human trafficking. Because of their threat to the American people, FBI’s top priority is to find them and pin each and every one of their members for their crimes; success of this mission would mean another win for the American people, just as good of a win as the arrest of Al Capone.

However, for FBI Special Agent Steve Rogers, it’s more personal. Infiltrating the family would mean avenging Bucky’s death, who died in the line of fire as an undercover agent. And Steve plans on finishing what Bucky started.

Famiglia per sempre.

summary: Marveltober Day 1 - First Film My first MCU film was Iron Man 3, so here's a little Mark 42 ! You can guess how lost I was right...
caption:
Marveltober Day 1 - First Film

My first MCU film was Iron Man 3, so here’s a little Mark 42 ! You can guess how lost I was right ww 

I loved everything I saw though, since the suits and brilliant effects to Tony and his priceless sarcasm. It was my introduction to the Marvel universe and it was definitely an experience! To this day I love Tony a lot and seeing his development throughout the films was definitely one of the best things ever~

title: Kinktober 2018
body:
read it on the AO3 at https://ift.tt/2NV1jST

by Aunt May (YokubouNoRain), YokubouNoRain

Desafío de 31 días llamado Kinktober que se realiza en el mes de octubre (por si ya sólo con el nombre no se habían dado cuenta).

Iba a hacer un desafío sólo MCU y otro sólo Ryokura… pero no puedo con mi vida y el alma no me alcanzaría para escribir 62 oneshots en un mes a dos por día. Forget it xD

Para identificar claramente la ship elegida, cada día va a estar estructurado por el nombre del tema elegido + el nombre de la pareja entre paréntesis :)

NOTA: Cada personaje/ kink seleccionado/ pairing será debidamente etiquetado en su día correspondiente ;)

***

Los personajes sobre los cuales leerán a continuación son propiedad de sus respectivos creadores (Marvel/ Marvel Studios/ Marvel Entertainment).
Las historias sí son de mi autoría. Por tal razón, no se permiten ni plagios, ni adaptaciones, ni adaptaplagios.
Disfuten de la lectura :)
